OL,3,CFamily say mother's death leaves
OL,4,C'massive hole' in their lives
OL,6,FThe family of a mother who died in the
OL,7,FScottish Borders say a 'massive hole
OL,8,Fhas been left' in their lives.
OL,10,FPolice Scotland was called to a
OL,11,Fproperty on Windram Road, Chirnside,
OL,12,Ffollowing reports that Megan Hughes,
OL,13,F31, was seriously injured just after
OL,14,F4.35am on 9 February 2025.
OL,16,FEmergency services pronounced her dead
OL,17,Fat the scene.
