OL,3,CFamily say mother's death leaves
OL,4,C'massive hole' in their lives
OL,6,FIn a statement, Megan's family said:
OL,7,F"Megan was a much-loved mother and
OL,8,Fdaughter. She was beautiful and
OL,9,Fcaring. This has left a massive hole
OL,10,Fin the family who are all absolutely
OL,11,Fdevastated."
OL,13,FCorey Dryden, 31, charged with murder,
OL,14,Fentered no plea when he appeared in
OL,15,Fprivate at Jedburgh Sheriff Court on
OL,16,F11 February 2025.
OL,18,FThe police are continuing their
OL,19,Finvestigation and appeal to anyone
OL,20,Fwith information to contact Police
OL,21,FScotland.
