OL,6,FThe defendant, who is remanded in
OL,7,Fcustody, will next appear in court
OL,8,Fwithin the next eight days.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Laura White said:
OL,11,F"Our thoughts are with the family and
OL,12,Ffriends of Megan at this difficult
OL,13,Ftime. We will continue to support them
OL,14,Fas the investigation continues."
